{"ID":"20260609133244-sftc5wd","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260609133244-sftc5wd","title":"2020年天津卷","type":"doc","updated":"20260609133343"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260609133305-p1q9o4k","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133305-p1q9o4k","updated":"20260609133305"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"“世界那么大，我想去看看”——这句流行语生动反映出人们在精神消费方面的愿望。纵观古今，人类从没有像今天这样(    )于旅游。一场完美的旅行，必须要选择一家称心如意的酒店。那么在古代，外出旅行或者出门办事，人们如何解决住宿问题呢?"}]},{"ID":"20260609133305-hew90hg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133305-hew90hg","updated":"20260609133305"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"西周早期，统治者在通往都城的道路上广修客舍，便于各地诸侯入朝纳贡和朝觐时休息。春秋战国时期，名为“传舍”或“逆旅”的客舍也出现了。西汉初期，各地均在交通要道上设立驿馆。南北朝时，许多王公贵族发现经营旅馆存在巨大商机，竞相建置，旅馆林立城中。唐朝繁盛，各国使者纷纷到大唐学习、取经。为了彰显唐人风度，官方旅馆的建设被提上日程。与此同时，民间旅馆的发展也相当可观。"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"u","TextMarkTextContent":"据《太平广记》记载了岐州富豪开设的私家旅馆，可以容纳千人食宿，不可谓世所罕见。"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"宋朝商品经济发达，在临安，私营旅馆临街而立，热闹非凡，尤其是西湖岸边的湖景旅馆，密密匝匝，令人( )。陆游那句“小楼一夜听春雨，深巷明朝卖杏花”，就是在杭州西湖砖街巷的一家湖景旅馆里写的。明初，全国要冲均设驿馆、递铺，“十里一铺、六十里一驿”的( )最常见。至晚清，中国的旅馆业走上了近代化之路。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133244-7lsl8pi","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609133244-7lsl8pi","updated":"20260609133319"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"题目"}]},{"ID":"20260609133319-7upqx99","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133319-7upqx99","updated":"20260609133319"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1．依次填入文中括号内的词语，最恰当的组是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260609133319-rouuwhl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133319-rouuwhl","updated":"20260609133319"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．热衷    左顾右盼    局面                                     B．热衷    眼花缭乱    格局"}]},{"ID":"20260609133319-w1uvv4g","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133319-w1uvv4g","updated":"20260609133319"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．热心    眼花缭乱    局面                                     D．热心    左顾右盼    格局"}]},{"ID":"20260609133319-79r2fzq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133319-79r2fzq","updated":"20260609133319"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2．文中画线句子有语病，下列修改正确的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260609133319-uwqbrjk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133319-uwqbrjk","updated":"20260609133319"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．据《太平广记》记载，岐州富豪开设的私家旅馆可以容纳千人食宿，不可谓世所罕见。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133319-svozrm1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133319-svozrm1","updated":"20260609133319"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．《太平广记》记载了岐州富豪开设私家旅馆，可以容纳千人食宿，不可谓世所罕见。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133319-zcsu6nz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133319-zcsu6nz","updated":"20260609133319"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．《太平广记》记载的岐州富豪开设私家旅馆，可以容纳千人食宿，可谓世所罕见。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133319-npjq7h9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133319-npjq7h9","updated":"20260609133319"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．据《太平广记》记载，岐州富豪开设的私家旅馆可以容纳千人食宿，可谓世所罕见。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133319-haprf3r","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133319-haprf3r","updated":"20260609133319"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3．下列与选文相关的文学常识，对应不正确的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260609133319-vb7glm6","Type":"NodeTable","TableAligns":[0,0,0,0,0],"Properties":{"colgroup":"||||","id":"20260609133319-vb7glm6","updated":"20260609133319"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableHead","Data":"thead","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableRow","Data":"tr","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"th","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"th","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"客舍青青柳色新"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"th","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"王维"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"th","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"《送元二使安西》"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"th","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"绝句"}]}]}]},{"Type":"NodeTableRow","Data":"tr","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"舍相如广成传"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"司马迁"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"《廉颇蔺相如列传》"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"散文"}]}]},{"Type":"NodeTableRow","Data":"tr","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"夫天地者万物之逆旅也"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"李白"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"《梦游天姥吟留别》"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"乐府诗"}]}]},{"Type":"NodeTableRow","Data":"tr","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"驿外断桥边，寂寞开无主"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"陆游"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"《卜算子·咏梅》"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"词"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260609133319-h3kzdgp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133319-h3kzdgp","updated":"20260609133319"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．A                                    B．B                                    C．C                                     D．D"}]},{"ID":"20260609133244-5q1amap","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609133244-5q1amap","updated":"20260609133331"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"答案"}]},{"ID":"20260609133244-zefgk25","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133244-zefgk25","updated":"20260609133331"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1．B    2．D    3．C"}]},{"ID":"20260609133244-pxweldo","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609133244-pxweldo","updated":"20260609133343"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"解析"}]},{"ID":"20260609133343-grr9rbw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133343-grr9rbw","updated":"20260609133343"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1．本题考查正确使用词语（包括熟语）的能力。解答此类题目，首先要明确题干的要求，即选出“正确”或“不正确”的一项，然后把握词语的意思，再结合语境辨析正误。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133343-1i0xlc5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133343-1i0xlc5","updated":"20260609133343"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"第一处，“热衷”，十分爱好（某种活动），犹醉心，沉迷，其后常搭配“于”，即“热衷于……”；“热心”，犹热情，谓有兴趣，肯尽力，积极主动，着重形容内心有兴趣，常用于对事；从语境来看，“人类从没有像今天这样(    )于旅游”，由“从没有像今天这样”这一信息可知，此处应是说当今社会人们对旅游的沉迷，应使用“热衷”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133343-flpfgen","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133343-flpfgen","updated":"20260609133343"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"第二处，“左顾右盼”，指向左右两边看，形容得意、犹豫等神态；“眼花缭乱”，形容眼睛看见复杂纷繁的东西而感到迷乱，比喻事物复杂，无法辨清；结合语境“西湖岸边的湖景旅馆，密密匝臣”可知，此处是形容面对这些密密匝匝旅馆的感觉，应使用“眼花缭乱”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133343-gux89on","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133343-gux89on","updated":"20260609133343"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"第三处，“局面”，一个时期内，事情的状态、形势，规模；“格局”，结构和格式；从语境来看，语境是说“全国要冲”“十里一铺、六十里一驿”的结构格式，应使用“格局”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133343-tnjrz0a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133343-tnjrz0a","updated":"20260609133343"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选B。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133343-vjcgy9d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133343-vjcgy9d","updated":"20260609133343"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2．本题考查辨析并修改病句的能力。解答此类题目，应先浏览选项，排除有明显错误标志的句子，然后按照主谓宾的成分压缩句子，先观察主干部分，是否存在搭配不当、残缺等问题，再分析修饰成分。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133343-kdif2or","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133343-kdif2or","updated":"20260609133343"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"“据《太平广记》记载了岐州富豪开设的私家旅馆，可以容纳千人食宿，不可谓世所罕见”，第一个问题，成分残缺，“可以容纳……”缺少主语，可以删除“据”，并把“了”改为“的”，让“私家旅馆”做后面句子的主语；第二个问题，“不可谓世所罕见”滥用否定词导致语义表达反了，“不可谓”意思是“不可以说是、不可以称为”，“世所罕见”意思是“在整个世界上都很少看到过。比喻特别稀有,非常珍贵”，语境要表达的意思是岐州富豪所开的私家旅馆是世所罕见的，但多了“不”，让句意表达反了，可以删除“不”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133343-4hvfza4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133343-4hvfza4","updated":"20260609133343"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A项，“不可谓世所罕见” 滥用否定词导致语义表达反了；"}]},{"ID":"20260609133343-hoz3q83","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133343-hoz3q83","updated":"20260609133343"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B项，结构混乱，前面句子的主语是《太平广记》，而“可以容纳”的主语应是“私家旅馆”，偷换主语；“不可谓世所罕见”滥用否定词导致语义表达反了；"}]},{"ID":"20260609133343-n3nmdnd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133343-n3nmdnd","updated":"20260609133343"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C项，“岐州富豪开设私家旅馆，可以容纳千人食宿”搭配不当，前一句的主语是“岐州富豪”，而“容纳千人食宿”的应该是“私家旅馆”，可以在“开设”后面添加“的”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133343-ejeza9a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133343-ejeza9a","updated":"20260609133343"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选D。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133343-l3jd6pc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133343-l3jd6pc","updated":"20260609133343"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3．本题考查学生识记文学常识的能力。解答此类试题，考生在课内学习的时候要注意识记，尤其要关注作者、朝代、国籍、自豪、代表作品、文学成就、文学流派等。本题要求选择“与选文相关的文学常识，对应不正确的一项”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133343-s16zn6t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133343-s16zn6t","updated":"20260609133343"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C项，“夫天地者万物之逆旅也——李白——《梦游天姥吟留别》——乐府诗”错误，“夫天地者万物之逆旅也”出自李白《春夜宴从弟桃花园序》，不是出自《梦游天姥吟留别》。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133343-7rr699e","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133343-7rr699e","updated":"20260609133343"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选C。"}]}]}